(412, 49, 'details_1_content', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Design, develop, and maintain automated test scripts for mobile and web applications.</li>\r\n 	<li>Utilize testing frameworks and tools to automate functional, regression, and performance tests.</li>\r\n 	<li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to understand testing requirements and ensure comprehensive test coverage.</li>\r\n 	<li>Execute automated tests across various operating system environments (Windows, macOS, Linux) to validate application compatibility.</li>\r\n 	<li>Integrate automated tests into continuous integration/continuous deployment (CI/CD) pipelines.</li>\r\n 	<li>Identify, analyze, and report software defects and collaborate with developers to ensure timely resolutions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Stay abreast of industry best practices and emerging tools in test automation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide mentorship and training to team members on automation testing practices.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
